Declare @UrunTID int

Declare xxxx Cursor Local For
Select  S.UrunTID From IT06_Stoklar S
Where S.StokTipID = 1 And ISNULL(S.IsImportData,0) = 0 Order By S.UrunTID asc

Open xxxx
Fetch Next From xxxx Into @UrunTID
While @@FETCH_STATUS=0 Begin

	Exec PSP06_OtoUrunKoduIplik @UrunTID = @UrunTID
	
	
	Fetch Next From xxxx Into @UrunTID
End
Close xxxx
Deallocate xxxx

Go
